		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row2"><span class="name"><a name="71043"></a><b>Anderin the Swiftbow</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails">Scout<br /><br /><br />Joined: 19 Feb 2004<br />Posts: 4<br /></span><br /></td>
		<td class="row2" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
			<tr>
				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=71043&amp;sid=498203192eeb898fe38a403fb1ee410b#71043"><img src="templates/Chronicles/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Tue Nov 30, 2004 6:13 am<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: </span></td>
				<td valign="top" align="right" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=71043&amp;sid=498203192eeb898fe38a403fb1ee410b"><img src="templates/Chronicles/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
